  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Ascovilla is an elegant hotel enjoying a quiet location in its own gardens and just 3 minute’s walk from the lakefront promenade and Piazza. With well-equipped rooms and good facilities, including lovely gardens, outdoor pool and small spa area, it provides a relaxing retreat, with quick access to the boats for when you want to explore.</p>]]></description>
